message.body: Hey, so Michael is not responding to my question about what time you're all planning to meet up. Do you know?
Hey, are you getting my texts?

Um I don't know. The last text I got was yesterday about the meet up time. I actually got that text an hour after you sent it, and Michael said he answered you. I never got a chance to answer you back.
No worries. I wasn't sure if you got mine since I never got an answer either. But at least we know it works!
